            <img src="#" alt="" />
            <h1>Take part in the Festival 2011 selection </h1>
            <p>The entry forms for films and projects (20<sup>th</sup> December) are online.</p>
            <a href="http://www.annecy.org/news:a182" class="btn_action" title="Read more">+ Read more</a>
