             <h3><img src="http://www.annecy.org/resources/interface/picto_zoom.png" alt="" />Animation Focus</h3>
              <h1>e-magiciens conference</h1>
              <p>The international Animation Film Festival favourite was awarded to three students making up the crew of "Chimères": Bastien Belvaux, Noé Giuliani et Juliette Oberndorfer.</p>
              <a href="http://www.annecy.org/news:a180" class="btn_action" title="Read more">+ Read more</a>
            </div>
            <div class="blc_oeuil">
             <h3><img src="http://www.annecy.org/resources/interface/picto_oeuil.png" alt="" />CITIA News</h3>
              <h1>Forum Blanc: Animation & Cross-media</h1>
              <p>Focused on the question of cross-media developments and aimed at imagery professionals, the second edition of the Forum Blanc will take place from 12<sup>th</sup> to 14<sup>th</sup> January 2011.
<br />
<strong>Deadline for Forum Blanc registration: 18<sup>th</sup> December 2010.</strong></p>
              <a href="http://www.annecy.org/news:a181" class="btn_action" title="Read more">+ Read more</a>
